reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is an excellent little device for an exceptional price. Easily backs up and transfers all of my photos, videos, files and music. Love the plug and play feature as well!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This 1 TB memory stick is exactly what I needed. I'm a content creator and my phone is getting kind of full so I bought this to help free up some space on my phone. It is easy to use. You have to plug it into your phone and then download the app. Then you have to go to your settings and find the memory stick in your general/about settings. It has created a ton more free space on my phone so now it can back up. The memory you get for the price is GREAT. 1 TB will hold so much and I'm so thankful that I took my chance on this memory stick. If you have been debating on getting one then I will say, it won't be a mistake and will serve many purposes. 5 of 5!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy to use and a ton of space
reviews.reviewText: I just got this 1TB flash drive a week ago and so far, I’m impressed with how much room this has. I use this to hold my pictures and videos since my phone doesn’t have a lot of memory. I was also pleased with how easy it was to use. My only issue, and why I gave this four stars, was with the directions that came with it. The font is so small even for someone that has good eyesight. I took pictures of each page and zoomed in to be able to read it. Overall, not bad for the price point!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Versatile, Protected, Choice of Color, and Attractive
reviews.reviewText: This flash drive is exceptional because its versatility is on par with my multifaceted technology needs; for instance, I have an iPhone, Android phone, and I use a desktop computer at the library from time-to-time. Each of those products have a different type of port, this one Flashdrive can be used with all three types. It is small, attractive and it comes in different colors. Also, it is packaged in a protective little lined tin and the tin is ensconced in a small ziplock plastic baggie. I love the protective forethought (from moisture and shock). I work in construction indoors and outdoors. I don’t have to worry about my little Flashdrive getting damaged if I forget about it in my pocket.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Product lives up to description
reviews.reviewText: I NEVER write product reviews on Amazon, but for the Auamoz 1TB Thumb Drive, I felt obligated. It arrived on time, and when I plugged it into my iPhone (after downloading the app) I was able to transfere hundreds of pics from my phone, to this tiny powerhouse and free up all that space on my phone. Not to mention the fact that since it's a true 1TB of storage, I was able to copy ALL my important documents on my MacBook, my ENTIRE music collection AND all DVD's that I've collected through the years. THis is a great product and I highly recommend it to anyone needed extra storage space. :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Too much time to get it started
reviews.reviewText: I rated a three because of the fast delivery. I'm disappointed in how long it takes to format and/or to get this up and running. I've spent at least 30 minutes trying to get this to sync with my phone. There aren't many ways to insert the connector. I've searched YouTube for videos and what I have found does not work at all. One would think a small task of inserting a USB would be easy, but it has not proven to be. I was excited to receive it in the mail, but I'll be packing it right up to send back. Hopefully the next one I purchase comes with better instruction and the next steps of when/if it does not work.

reviews.reviewTitle: It works well on my IPhone 13 PRO MAX.
reviews.reviewText: This flash drive actually can backup all my files from my IPHONE to flash drive.Setup is just Download the Y-DISK APP, then PLUG and PLAY, as I did not have to read all the instructions provided, to backup all my videos, pictures, and documents. The backup from my 256G iphone to 512G Flash drive takes about an hour.I am surprised that it worked, but I think the iPhone have to be unlocked. It will only backup pictures that I have taken, and will not work on any contents from itunes.This is my only second day usage, so far, I am happy with my purchase.The only thing that I do not like is having to remove my Iphone from the case or the lightening connector will not connect properly. I will need to buy an extender.
